name: Dog Cookies Large Box
description:
24 pieces of our  hand-cut Canine Confections. We use only the best, organic ingredients. Delicious and fresh baked. Gourmet dog cookies for any event. 24 cookies in each box. (Assortments may vary slightly in press and style.)

Each cookie is organic, chemical free, wheat free, meat free and corn free. No added sugar or salt too!
